headline: Wells Fargo Keeps Neutral Stance on Dollar General (DG) Amid Diverging Retail Trends
summary: Dollar General Corporation (NYSE:DG) is included among the 20 Best Performing Dividend Stocks in 2025. On December 19, Wells Fargo raised its price target on Dollar General Corporation (NYSE:DG) to $125 from $115 and kept an Equal Weight rating.
